 Syntax:
>FROM-used to declare base image
ex:FROM Python
>LABEL-used to add description about image.
>MAINTAINER- used to define author details.
>ADD-used to copy files from local to container and it will be download the files from internet and send those files to container.
>WORKDIR-used to set a default path for container.
>COPY-used to copy files from local to container.
>ARG-used to pass variables while we build image,these vars will not be available inside the container,we can overwrite these values while we build the image.
>ENV-used to pass variables while we build image.these vars will be available inside the container.
>RUN-used to execute the commands.
>EXPOSE-used to expose the port number.

